The paper discusses the use of machine learning for resource management in cellular and IoT networks, which falls under the category of networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also extensively discusses the use of deep learning and traditional machine learning techniques, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the challenges and solutions related to resource allocation and management, which falls under the category of control systems (cs.SY) and information theory (cs.IT).
